Exercise 9 - Async JS, Promises, Async/Await

Objective

Fetch event data using asynchronous JavaScript.

Scenario

Fetch event data from a mock API and display it on the webpage.

Tasks

- Fetch events from a mock JSON endpoint.
- Use `.then()` and `.catch()` to handle the response.
- Rewrite the same functionality using `async/await`.
- Display a loading message while fetching data.

